    "description": {
      "zh": "一款可调式通用夜视仪支架系统，由 Wilcox 公司设计制造。该支架具备应急防卡挂设计，在遭受相当力度的冲击时会自动断裂分离头盔，避免使用者受到严重伤害。兼容大部分夜视仪转接器与头盔接口。灰褐色版本。",
      "en": "A universal adjustable night vision mounting system manufactured by Wilcox. Features a breakaway lever that disconnects under stress to prevent user injury. Compatible with most night vision shrouds and adapters. Coyote version."
